source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_00<tab>Woolnix is eyeing you with obvious interest.

TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_01<tab>Woolnix is fretting about the great swarm of tarantula hawks in the Collectors' Quarter. He does not feel safe guarding the gate whilst they are so near. Thus, he bids you slay three, in hopes that they will no more encroach upon his position.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_01<tab>Woolnix vous demande d'éliminer les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E090302 /var> qui le harcèlent. Cherchez au quartier des Collectionneurs et éliminez trois de ces nuisibles.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_02<tab>You have struck down three tarantula hawks. Deliver tidings of your victory to Woolnix near the Cenotaph.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez vaillamment terrassé les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E090302 /var> perturbatrices. Retournez voir Woolnix pour empocher votre récompense.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_03<tab>Woolnix reveals to you that he was stung by a tarantula hawk, and, driven mad by the pain, left his post. Now that there are a few less hovering about nearby, however, he believes he can do his duty in safety.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_03<tab>Grâce à vous, Woolnix pourra continuer son travail de sentinelle en se contentant de chasser seulement les intrus, et plus les guêpes.

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_000<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander has good arm for fighty-tool, yes?
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_000<tab>Psssh... L'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> a l'air fort<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_001<tab>Please, kill tarantula hawks for Woolnix. They are swarming in Collectors' Quarter, giving Woolnix terrible fright when gate guarding. Kill three, and Woolnix is feeling safer!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_001<tab>Woolnix aimerait que quelqu'un abatte trois <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E090302 /var> pour lui, au quartier des Collectionneurs<var 1D /var>! Allez, quoi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_010<tab>With so many tarantula hawks in Collectors' Quarter, Woolnix worried about gate guarding in safety.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_010<tab>Woolnix aimerait que quelqu'un abatte trois <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E090302 /var> pour lui, au quartier des Collectionneurs<var 1D /var>! Allez, quoi<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_020<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander does great favor for Woolnix! In truth, Woolnix ran away when attacked by bugs. Woolnix was scolded for leaving gate unwatched, but this is unfair!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_020<tab>Psssh, pssh... Beau travail, beau travail<var 1D /var>! Woolnix est re<var 16 /var>con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>sant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_021<tab>Woolnix was stung by tarantula hawk, ran because pain was driving Woolnix mad! <sigh> But now tarantula hawks are fewer, Woolnix can patrol in peace.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_021<tab>Woolnix se fait tout le temps piquer par ces sales insectes<var 1D /var>! Woolnix s'est enfui... et Woolnix a abandonné sa garde et du coup s'est fait gronder<var 1D /var>! Moins il y aura d'insectes, moins Woolnix aura de problèmes<var 1D /var>! Même les gardes ont le droit d'avoir peur des petites bêtes<var 1D /var>!
